                    ACCEPT ATENCAO-REGISTO-LOCK1
                 END-IF

              CLOSE UNIDADES
           END-PERFORM
           EXIT SECTION.

       REGISTAR-PROF SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *    REGISTO DA SILA E NOME DO DOCENTE NO HORARIO.
      ******************************************************************
           PERFORM WITH TEST AFTER UNTIL VERDADEIRO = "S"
              MOVE SPACES TO REG-PROF, VERDADEIRO
              DISPLAY LIMPAR-LISTA1
              DISPLAY NOTA-SCREEN
              DISPLAY LIMPAR-LINES
              ACCEPT PROF-SCREEN
